<header>Waterfield Government</header>
<main>
  <h1>Department of Waterfield Fairgrounds</h1>
  <p>The Waterfield Fairgrounds serve as the central location for community events, fairs, and festivals throughout the year. The department manages the scheduling, maintenance, and facilities to ensure a safe and welcoming environment for residents and visitors alike.</p>
  <p>The Fairgrounds include ample parking, outdoor event spaces, exhibition halls, and amenities to accommodate a wide variety of activities. Coordination with local organizations helps to bring diverse events to the village.</p>
  <p>For reservations, event planning, or more information, please contact the Fairgrounds Department at <a href="mailto:fairgrounds@waterfieldmi.gov">fairgrounds@waterfieldmi.gov</a> or call (555) 123-4567.</p>
</main>
